      <title>Dialektik 0.2.0</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>Dialektik 0.2.0</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Improved cross-network room connectivity and join request handling.</li>
          <li>Added reliable in-app rejection notifications and native join request notifications.</li>
          <li>Improved collaborative document synchronization and session stability.</li>
        </ul>
